Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和小林吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,鼓肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:29.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是夜晚很暗讓人發困  飛到發亮的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:50.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好多建築
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,595日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好  請問你需要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是日本的貨幣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我們這裡不流通日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不收日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,語言不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是一個人嗎  你媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去找你媽媽拿美元過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.75,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,為什麼你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.21,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.79,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,我一直很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.30,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你為什麼就是不明白  這太羞恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.13,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,我怎麼不明白了  我跟你講清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,熱狗又不會跑掉 所以不用急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等你回來  我會給你打折的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.68,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,都說了肯定是我更喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.10,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,明明是我更喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦  突然發呆了沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:26.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:29.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不使用我們國家的貨幣是買不了東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,錢用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡人好少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,站住  你個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:52.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才不要被你們抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我被人追啊  他們是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說要救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別擋路  閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個小鬼是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然敢把邁克爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我跟你說  邁克爾今天只是肚子不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:30.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你明明還是個小孩  但是好強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說起來這裡是紐約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我叫柯蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:56.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:57.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他們為什麼要追你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是被他們綁架來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他們好像是黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,黑手黨  是壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後我找到機會逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我爸爸是大企業的總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和那些黑手黨是死對頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比起這種事  我們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你覺得是小事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好閒  我們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也是  去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,作為回禮  想吃什麼我請你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:45.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:52.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正好  現在我也不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,黑卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我們這裡不支持刷卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我沒帶太多現金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說起來  我還是第一次來紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,平時只能在宅子附近轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊很有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和才川一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:22.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她一直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那孩子沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們總是在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的人都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次和朋友們像這樣放開玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我該回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:47.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事的  才剛剛天黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:54.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是和小林吵架然後離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不過是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要回去  跟她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你回去沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒準她還在生你的氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,萬一道歉了她也不原諒你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:29.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我更怕失去這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:14.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還以為綁架一個離家出走的小女孩會很簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感覺需要懲罰一下你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,綁緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明白  邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她可是重要的商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一隻手而已  應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:41.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想回家  如果沒有離家出走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  停電嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:48.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去看看電閘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  這是在夢裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還是說我已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜你是從天堂來接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊的家在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我家在明尼蘇達  大概在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在一個大湖的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毛茸茸的  好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聽我說  康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也是離家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,柯蘿伊也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我和爸爸吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:26.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:28.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算她們生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算你說討厭她們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她們也會跟我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果是這樣的人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還能再見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒問題  我告訴你住址
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有住址的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看看你  都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,應當道歉的對象不是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾大人  小林在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經想好等她醒過來以後怎麼道歉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和小林如出一轍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.92,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：紐約五大區曼哈頓、布魯克林、皇后區、布朗克斯、史丹頓島的首字母縮寫。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我全都看在眼裡
Comment: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第十話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.98,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}康娜的暑假（雙語配音！？）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那小林我也去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.71,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你能在北海道本地吃到新鮮的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.21,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,我最推薦海膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林今天休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:45.13,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,這家餐廳是現殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對  休息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.43,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,所以我就點了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:52.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\b1\c&H000000&\pos(305.333,140.334)\3c&HDBD548&}清爽！！早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:52.89,Kobayashi S2 - Comment Down,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&HE21A25&\bord1\blur3\b1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(877.333,191)}這個季節絕對想吃的{\c&H0F01DE&\fs55}海鮮{\fs45\c&HE21A25&}特輯!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:52.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\3c&H27BED9&\c&H24C5E4&\4c&H19346A&\shad5\bord0\pos(362.933,495.8)}海  膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.05,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,直到昨天都累死個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,加班地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.76,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你看這海膽的色澤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  加班地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.53,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,下面讓我們連線到金澤的小村小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.62,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,大家好  我是小村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.16,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,大家看這隊排的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾大人和伊露露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.42,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,這家店的豆沙餡蜜人氣很高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她們兩個都要打工到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.00,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,這就是我們今天要介紹的咖啡店甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林今天是要懶散度日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.22,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,那麼今天就讓我們進去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:23.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,懶散度日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.55,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,秘訣就是將黑糖漿用在豆沙餡蜜上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.64,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,大家快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:34.02,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\c&H4798E6&\bord3\3c&HDFDEEA&\pos(1066.933,162.267)\frz3.097}美食{\c&HD955ED&}特輯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:34.02,Kobayashi S2 - STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\c&HAEDD92&\3c&H132A22&\pos(1485.866,229.934)}老字號糯米餡蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜要去找才川玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.89,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,看看這光澤  濃稠的糖漿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川說今天開始和家裡一起去旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.77,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,不好意思那我就先嚐一口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.06,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,嗯  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那很閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.57,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,黑糖漿的口感很厚重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,餡蜜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.32,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,甜而不膩…完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.57,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,我好像知道為什麼這裡大排長龍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  我想吃西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.95,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,顯然這裡有很多女性都在排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,剛剛有出現過西瓜相關的要素嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.41,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,有些人還是從很遠的地方來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,昨天托爾大人買來了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你還看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就做為午飯後的甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,熱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了  吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我要開始做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜你能幫我看看樓下的郵箱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:38.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小番茄？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.79,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz310.9\3c&H5143BC&\c&H3E3E43&\bord3\pos(1288,131)\b1}家庭版
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.79,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 4 - Verticle,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3E3E43&\fs35\frz251.8\pos(821.333,299)}風味醇香彈牙爽口之絕品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.79,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3E3E43&\bord0\frz346.2\pos(998.667,757.667)}掛\N面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.79,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 4 - Verticle,,0,0,0,,{\frz252.3\c&H3E3E43&\pos(1124,360.334)}老字號匠心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好簡單
Comment: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/批發生薑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,航空郵件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,難道是你之前在美國認識的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:03.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她叫柯蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:06.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她說她想到我們家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.28,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3E3E43&\bord2\b0\fs50\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(505.333,261.667)\frz15.92}下次再一起玩吧  克洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以帶她來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:11.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是期待
Comment: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,麥茶喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再不去買就只剩牛奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒辦法  出去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜戴帽子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,戴上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:44.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:48.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,邊走邊想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,走呀走  走呀走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是能做成圖畫日記就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也順便找找自主研究的選題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是能找到什麼選題就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:14.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾大人說可以研究小林可能會喜歡的異世界食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,換一個選題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,住在下水管道裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下水管道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是螞蟻洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不對  是為人類而造的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在這下面有疏水用的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在城市裡縱橫交錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那這種井蓋也有很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,超級多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要找這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自主研究嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是附近常見的樣式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:12.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只有這個是四角的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是消防栓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個也是同一類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但又有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小…小康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Comment: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:31.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/咖啡
Comment: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:31.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/真田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對家裡蹲來說是一次很好的鍛鍊
Comment: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/咖啡
Comment: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/真田
Comment: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/消防栓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍吃冰淇淋也會頭疼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林的好像也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要嚐一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼  有顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還有這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明一直都住在這裡卻還有不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是哪個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是恬靜君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜你知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在坊間很有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,坊間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:33.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:34.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,筆記本也保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我被淋的好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這招是什麼  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這也算是夏日才有的風物之詩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,風物之詩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雨雨雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,酸性雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是首不吉利的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,轟雷暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,嘩嘩啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,完蛋完蛋  器材要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小心腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是恬靜君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,注意頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別推了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這就是下水管道畫的原型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,請把頭低一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,七星瓢蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是被沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:43.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:44.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有家的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,確實是彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雨完全停了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾他們也快回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:16.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:25.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次我要把相機也帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,煮飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們倆都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:43.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:45.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.08,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,快煮飯
